The '''Morish''' were a short, furry, loud-voiced species from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Morishim]] in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]]. During the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] reign, a secret communications centre was established in a cave on Morishim. After the Empire pulled out, a Morish known as the [[Old Recluse]] found the abandoned communications link, and used its newsfeeds to fool others into believing he had [[Wikipedia:clairvoyance|clairvoyant]] abilities.

Morish were perfectly capable of speaking [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], but those Morish who did speak Basic often pretended not to.

